## Using CSS

Ek "styles.css" naam ki file banao, jisme neeche diya hua code likho. Ab aap iss file ko uss folder mei save karo jaha apki HTML course ki index.html files stored hain.

```css
body {
    background-color: lightblue;
}
h1 {
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
}
p {
    font-family: verdana;
    color: darkgray;
    font-size: 20px;
}
```

